    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to develop a registry tool used for the management and
      care of patients with eosinophilic disorders, and create a research resource that will
      provide further insights into these disorders.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
